</span>"},{"pid":"aa353971559e2fb21b084c91d284ff77cf9c1e5e","tid":604911,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:33:54.000Z","msg":"工賊會害左香港幾耐，呢條數落到地府都有排同佢班仆街計"},{"pid":"cb6713ca57935cf4c2a3c10398ac36e6262ac036","tid":604911,"uid":86980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:41:27.000Z","msg":"陳婉嫻可唔可以出嚟解釋下?"},{"pid":"3fb23f3bf65f632a0f7a60aeb76a904a7cc1bdfb","tid":604911,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T16:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2255ac10e00022672af5747b29b6e1d3b686e6a8","tid":604911,"uid":74012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"02a953b9db18139096b66a2cea97c1af2ae91708","tid":604911,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cd39cbaf54a11d2b62b3a5a8f76b797439bf1b5","tid":604911,"uid":16676,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T07:57:03.000Z","msg":"呢個正苦, 識<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>改企業利得稅兩級制<br />\n但又趁機會同企業傾條件</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大把稅收, 盈餘下, <br />\n只要撥多d 錢落去MPF 對衝果度, 好快就成事<br />\n<br />\n<strong>垃圾預算案, 無能兼無腦會計財爺劏房波</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">反而MPF 對衝<br />\n全民退保, 醫保<br />\n勞工假<br />\n立法5天工作制<br />\n最高工時</span><br />\n<br />\n呢d 實事, 隨時仲簡單又唔去做, 推都唔撚推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T14:07:02.000Z","msg":"班仆街其實都知依d野<br />\n不過死都唔推玩鳩班港豬<br />\n不過班豬就沒感覺嘅<br />\n繼續返工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T19:30:01.000Z","msg":"根本香港商人/高層都是習近平<br />\n重視自身權力<br />\n<br />\n點會肯比你集體談判權<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再加埋同你講李卓人六四帶幾百萬上大陸被充工, 講多兩講妖魔化埋佢, 話佢出賣香港人之類唔好信佢"}]}